<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/b6ec42443332c9d4fccad02c2c52fbf82.png"></span><span>White Sparrow</span></dt><dd><div>Fills 100% of skill gauges at the start of quests<br>and increases the duration of debuff skills by<br>25%. In addition, using a skill will grant the user<br>a strength amp with a maximum team amp level<br>of three. After this amp is granted, this ability<br>will not grant it again for 30 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/1773f9fc2cee21b3daccbd539f0569eb2.png"></span><span>White Sparrow's Vow III</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to freeze and bog by<br>100%. When Leif is hit by an attack that would<br>have inflicted freeze or bog on him, his strength<br>is increased by 15% for 10 seconds.<br>This increase will not stack, and, after activating,<br>this buff cannot be activated again by the same<br>affliction for 15 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/8c5efd6ea1a6cf7dccb111f085a0c4242.png"></span><span>Flurry Strength & Poison Edge/Sting I</span></dt><dd><div>When the combo count is 10 or higher,<br>increases strength by 25%, the chances of<br>inflicting poison by 70%, and the duration<br>of poison inflicted on enemies by 30%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.</div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1636956000,update_time1636602049